      </span>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="62b93-102">当<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D>对象分配给<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D.Pivot%2A>属性<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D>对象，它会影响元素由单个操控器操作时，操作处理器如何计算旋转更改的元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-102">When a <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> object is assigned to the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D.Pivot%2A> property of a <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationProcessor2D> object, it affects how the manipulation processor calculates rotational changes to an element when the element is being manipulated by a single manipulator.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="62b93-103">如果多个操控器在操作过程应用于元素，则忽略 Pivot 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-103">If more than one manipulator is being applied to the element during manipulation, the Pivot property is ignored.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="62b93-104">在单操控器方案中，为所拖动，可以旋转元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-104">In a single-manipulator scenario, an element can rotate as it is being dragged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="62b93-105"><xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A>属性<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D>对象确定哪些解决问题，旋转元素的位置和<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A>操作处理器使用属性来计算旋转更改量。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> properties of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> object determine what position the element rotates around, and the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A> property is used by the manipulation processor to calculate the amount of rotational change.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="62b93-106">例如，如果单个操控器的外边缘的透视点附近，到元素的旋转更改为所拖动将非常大 （根据元素的大小）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-106">For instance, if the single manipulator is near the outer edge of the pivot point, the rotational change to the element as it is being dragged will be fairly large (depending upon the size of the element).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="62b93-107">如果操控器即将透视点的中心，将发生很少 （如果有） 旋转。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-107">If the manipulator is close to the center of the pivot point, very little (if any) rotation will occur.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="62b93-108">通常情况下，<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A>属性表示的元素进行操作，center 和<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A>属性到其最远的边缘表示从元素的中心的距离。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-108">Typically, the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> properties represent the center of the element that is being manipulated, and the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Radius%2A> property represents the distance from the center of the element to its farthest edge.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="62b93-109">在元素移动时，<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A>属性<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D>对象需要更新以便旋转会不断发生绕正确的点。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-109">As the element moves, the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> properties of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D> object need to be updated so that rotation will continue to occur around the proper point.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="62b93-110">下面的代码示例演示如何<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A>透视点的属性会更新为匹配的元素进行操作的中心。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="62b93-110">The following code example shows how the <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.X%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.Manipulations.ManipulationPivot2D.Y%2A> properties for a pivot point are updated to match the center of the element that is being manipulated.</span></span>  
  
